WEBVTT

01:38.120 --> 01:40.560
EPISODE 4

01:42.760 --> 01:45.360
Xiaoyang's mom will be home
in 10 minutes.

01:45.480 --> 01:46.480
Let's say hi before we go.

01:46.560 --> 01:48.560
Say hi to his mom? Why?

01:49.920 --> 01:52.480
Didn't you want to see his mom's car?

01:52.600 --> 01:54.760
Otherwise you'll accuse me
of faking the photo.

01:54.840 --> 01:56.240
It's okay.

01:58.640 --> 02:00.360
I already deleted the post.

02:01.440 --> 02:04.000
And I have to apologize to you.

02:04.880 --> 02:06.920
I'm sorry, Bei Weiwei.
It was a misunderstanding.

02:09.199 --> 02:11.240
Okay, I accept.

02:11.600 --> 02:13.560
That's it?

02:14.360 --> 02:15.760
What else should I do?

02:16.760 --> 02:17.880
You're not quite as I imagined.

02:19.120 --> 02:22.400
You should never judge a person
by mere assumption.

02:23.600 --> 02:26.360
Anyway, what happened to Xiaoyang's legs?

02:28.840 --> 02:30.720
- Car accident.
- Car accident?

02:32.280 --> 02:35.520
Xiaoyang lost his father
in that accident,

02:35.960 --> 02:39.320
along with the ability to stand.

02:39.400 --> 02:42.120
He seems quite cheerful. I didn't know...

02:43.960 --> 02:46.600
Is it suitable for you
to expose a kid that young to gaming?

02:48.040 --> 02:49.120
You got it wrong.

02:49.200 --> 02:52.400
I didn't expose him to gaming.
It was he who showed me.

02:52.840 --> 02:54.120
He showed you?

02:54.720 --> 02:58.520
Yeah, I used to have
a bad impression of gaming, too.

02:58.600 --> 03:00.160
I thought it was a waste of time.

03:00.920 --> 03:03.760
When Xiaoyang's mom found me,

03:03.840 --> 03:06.040
she hoped I could wean him off gaming.

03:06.880 --> 03:09.920
I thought, in order to change
his perception,

03:10.000 --> 03:12.000
I should know what gaming is all about.

03:12.680 --> 03:14.600
So I tried it.

03:15.160 --> 03:17.760
My view of gaming unexpectedly
changed completely.

03:18.200 --> 03:20.600
So you fell in love with gaming?

03:21.840 --> 03:25.880
Gaming is a world
that is neither good nor bad.

03:25.960 --> 03:28.600
Everyone just approaches it differently.

03:30.240 --> 03:34.000
Perhaps there are many people
like Xiaoyang,

03:34.480 --> 03:36.160
who can't go outside.

03:36.600 --> 03:37.960
Gaming provides opportunities

03:38.040 --> 03:41.560
for him to see more sceneries
and meet more people.

03:41.920 --> 03:43.720
From this perspective,

03:43.800 --> 03:46.320
gaming is quite meaningful. No?

03:48.320 --> 03:50.800
My only impact on Xiaoyang

03:50.920 --> 03:55.880
is perhaps that I've steered his interests
more toward game development.

03:56.560 --> 03:58.200
Xiaoyang has changed me, too.

03:58.440 --> 04:03.360
My goal in life, at least for now,
is to become a game designer.

04:19.399 --> 04:22.200
Where's Xiaoling and Sisi?
You're by yourself?

04:23.440 --> 04:25.760
Xiaoling is with Dazhong, of course.

04:25.840 --> 04:28.280
Sisi is always out and about nowadays.

04:29.040 --> 04:31.880
What's this?
You're playing "A Chinese Ghost Story"?

04:31.960 --> 04:34.920
That's right. I have to cram for it,

04:35.000 --> 04:38.360
because of the lie
I told at the interview.

04:38.680 --> 04:41.160
You didn't get busted. Why worry?

04:41.240 --> 04:42.440
What if I get the internship?

04:43.360 --> 04:46.000
If I can't answer anything they ask me,

04:46.080 --> 04:47.480
they'll know I'm a fraud.

04:47.560 --> 04:49.920
I'm worried about ruining
your reputation as Luwei Weiwei!

04:52.920 --> 04:54.000
Fine. Wait, I'll show you.

04:54.080 --> 04:56.840
No way! I don't want to be
on the same server as you.

04:57.360 --> 05:00.320
The old server is swarming
with seasoned players.

05:00.400 --> 05:02.000
A newbie like me can never catch up.

05:02.200 --> 05:05.400
So, I wisely chose a new server.

05:05.480 --> 05:08.240
The new server is called Lady Fairy.

05:08.680 --> 05:10.600
It suits my elegance.

05:10.680 --> 05:13.240
Also, we're all newbies,
so it's easier to communicate.

05:13.320 --> 05:14.760
I won't lose at the starting line.

05:15.320 --> 05:19.320
Fine. Since you've decided to take on
a new server on your own,

05:19.400 --> 05:20.240
ask me, if have any questions.

05:23.520 --> 05:25.520
IN-GAME COUPLES BATTLE CHAMPIONSHIP

05:30.680 --> 05:33.560
Why is there so little news
on the championship?

05:34.280 --> 05:36.840
I wonder when it will formally begin.

05:42.480 --> 05:46.760
What? Video Drama Contest?

05:50.400 --> 05:51.520
Zhenshui Wuxiang?

06:24.320 --> 06:26.080
Don't be scared. I'm here.

06:32.840 --> 06:34.240
I'm so glad you came.

06:34.640 --> 06:39.000
What is this thing called love?
Why am I moved to live and die by it?

06:39.200 --> 06:40.400
Don't say that dreadful word!

06:40.640 --> 06:43.560
We'll return to Jinling City.
You must get well.

06:44.040 --> 06:47.240
My heart's broken
and my tears have dried up.

06:47.320 --> 06:49.200
Why do you ignore me?

06:52.200 --> 06:56.280
LIUWAI WAIWAI

06:58.280 --> 06:59.600
Liuwai Waiwai?

07:11.520 --> 07:15.000
Stop! Why do you prefer her?

07:15.080 --> 07:17.920
Do you know how sad it makes me?

07:18.640 --> 07:22.720
I won't listen! Don't go!
This time, I won't let you slip away!

07:23.520 --> 07:27.840
Social formalities have created
too many obstacles for you and me.

07:28.280 --> 07:30.400
You're leaving me, just like this?

07:30.480 --> 07:33.120
What have I done wrong?

07:33.880 --> 07:37.320
All I ever want is a pure, innocent love.

07:38.200 --> 07:41.640
Remember this, all of you!
I'll make you pay for this!

07:52.920 --> 07:56.880
What have I done wrong?

08:01.600 --> 08:02.560
You...

08:08.160 --> 08:09.200
Are you okay?

08:09.920 --> 08:10.800
Let's go.

08:23.600 --> 08:26.960
Liuwai Waiwai? Luwei Weiwei!

08:28.600 --> 08:30.160
What do you get out of this?

08:33.799 --> 08:36.280
Is veiled defamation that fun for you?

08:36.799 --> 08:38.200
I didn't think you'd be like that.

08:43.679 --> 08:44.520
What's wrong?

08:46.040 --> 08:50.280
It's nothing. People are evil.
I'm going to bed.

08:59.600 --> 09:00.440
What's up?

09:00.520 --> 09:04.280
Hello, Nai? We've got a situation.
Go check out the game forum.

09:04.480 --> 09:06.360
Zhenshui Wuxiang made a video,

09:06.440 --> 09:09.160
throwing shade at Mrs. Nai.
It's infuriating.

09:09.440 --> 09:11.440
Yugong is on a tirade on the forum.

09:12.600 --> 09:14.000
Okay, I'll be right there.

09:14.760 --> 09:16.120
What?

09:16.960 --> 09:18.160
Yugong! Houzi!

09:18.240 --> 09:20.440
Throw the socks into the laundry room!

09:20.520 --> 09:21.800
Nai is coming here!

09:22.520 --> 09:23.560
Nai is coming here!

09:28.080 --> 09:29.560
Hurry. Into the bins.

09:30.560 --> 09:32.880
Whose sock is this? It reeks!

09:32.960 --> 09:33.800
Is it yours, Hao Mei?

09:35.640 --> 09:37.720
It's not mine! It's Yu Banshan's!

09:37.800 --> 09:39.240
- Why is it mine?
- It's Yu Banshan's!

09:39.320 --> 09:40.160
I don't have socks!

09:40.240 --> 09:43.080
Whose underwear is this? Yours?

09:43.160 --> 09:46.000
No! It's not mine! It's yours!

09:46.240 --> 09:49.400
- How come it's mine?
- It's Hao Mei's! Yes!

10:04.200 --> 10:05.800
Zhenshui Wuxiang is so narcissistic!

10:05.880 --> 10:08.240
He's deluded into thinking
Mrs. Nai fancies him.

10:08.480 --> 10:12.040
He should take a look at himself.
He's no match for Nai!

10:12.360 --> 10:15.240
Is that narcissism?
That's extreme narcissism.

10:15.360 --> 10:17.960
I hear this guy is a rich kid.

10:18.400 --> 10:19.600
He's okay-looking.

10:20.600 --> 10:22.880
Nai doesn't post his photos online.

10:22.960 --> 10:24.160
If he did,

10:24.240 --> 10:27.520
who'd believe Mrs. Nai fancied Zhenshui?

10:28.040 --> 10:30.480
A gamer from our server
wrote a post that said

10:30.560 --> 10:32.600
Mrs. Nai was dumped by Zhenshui Wuxiang.

10:32.680 --> 10:35.160
I got so mad.
I gave him a virtual tongue-lashing.

10:35.240 --> 10:36.320
That shut him up.

10:36.400 --> 10:38.520
Why bother with that?

10:38.640 --> 10:41.080
Nai, just hack the post.

10:41.160 --> 10:43.720
No, leave it.

10:44.040 --> 10:45.640
We'll solve this civilly.

10:45.760 --> 10:47.880
Civilly? How?

10:52.840 --> 10:54.200
Wait for him to log on tomorrow.

11:21.120 --> 11:25.160
Gaming is a world
that is neither good or bad.

11:25.240 --> 11:27.920
Everyone just approaches it differently.

11:29.520 --> 11:33.240
Perhaps there are many people
like Xiaoyang,

11:33.920 --> 11:35.520
who can't go outside.

11:36.000 --> 11:37.320
Gaming provides opportunities

11:37.400 --> 11:40.920
for him to see more sceneries
and meet more people.

11:41.280 --> 11:43.000
From this perspective,

11:43.080 --> 11:45.000
gaming is quite meaningful. No?

12:35.440 --> 12:36.880
Hello, Bei Weiwei!

12:38.240 --> 12:40.200
You're jogging, too, Cao Guang?

12:40.280 --> 12:42.880
I saw you beeping four cards earlier.

12:44.960 --> 12:45.960
Are you going to expose me again?

12:47.600 --> 12:49.680
I only do this occasionally,
for my fellow students.

12:50.440 --> 12:51.520
You think I got nothing better to do?

12:52.760 --> 12:55.000
You're not so trustworthy,
based on your history.

12:56.040 --> 12:58.000
Thanks, though. I'll get back to jogging.

12:58.080 --> 13:00.880
Wait! Can I treat you to a meal?

13:02.200 --> 13:04.440
No, thanks. I'm eating with my roommates.

13:04.720 --> 13:07.440
When are you free?
I'll treat you to breakfast.

13:08.240 --> 13:10.520
I want to apologize for the other day.

13:10.600 --> 13:12.240
A simple "sorry" doesn't cut it.

13:13.160 --> 13:15.320
It's fine, really.
It's all cleared up now.

13:15.960 --> 13:17.840
Just don't do it again.

13:18.280 --> 13:20.080
If I went back in time, I'd do it again.

13:21.280 --> 13:23.000
- What?
- No.

13:23.080 --> 13:27.040
I mean, I'm glad that incident happened.

13:27.120 --> 13:29.880
No, I mean, I'm glad to have met you.

13:37.880 --> 13:39.920
I have another question.

13:41.480 --> 13:42.480
Do you have a boyfriend?

13:45.400 --> 13:49.000
I don't have a boyfriend,
nor do I plan to have one.

13:49.120 --> 13:52.120
- I'll get back to jogging. Bye-bye!
- Bye-bye.

14:42.080 --> 14:45.280
Today, we'll be analyzing
Hollywood genre films,

14:45.520 --> 14:48.200
by using the case of Titanic.

14:48.280 --> 14:50.800
I'm sure all of you have seen the movie.

14:51.480 --> 14:53.040
This movie was co-funded

14:53.160 --> 14:56.240
by American company, 20th Century Fox

14:56.320 --> 15:00.200
and American company, Paramount Pictures.

15:00.280 --> 15:02.960
The production began in 1994.

15:04.120 --> 15:05.640
This movie

15:06.080 --> 15:09.360
clearly embodies features
from two different genres,

15:09.640 --> 15:13.360
romance and disaster.

15:14.440 --> 15:16.800
This is my seat. Scoot over!

15:16.880 --> 15:17.920
I got here first.

15:19.640 --> 15:20.480
Cao Guang?

15:21.920 --> 15:25.440
You know me?
I still won't give you my seat.

15:26.320 --> 15:29.640
I was here first.
I only left to get breakfast.

15:30.000 --> 15:31.960
See? My book is still here.

15:37.200 --> 15:39.600
You'd better scoot, before I get riled.

15:39.680 --> 15:41.960
Listen, I scare myself, when I'm mad.

15:48.920 --> 15:50.080
Just let me in, okay?

16:10.200 --> 16:12.360
Lady, are you on a slide?

16:12.760 --> 16:14.800
The chair is broken! Can't you see?

16:15.240 --> 16:17.280
I forgot to check my horoscope!

16:17.360 --> 16:19.600
Poor me! Why did I have to run into him?

16:19.800 --> 16:21.760
You're blaming others for your tardiness?

16:24.680 --> 16:29.640
Lady, I'm a foreign languages major,
yet I failed to understand your English.

16:29.800 --> 16:30.640
Was that a dialect?

16:31.440 --> 16:32.520
Shut up, I say!

16:44.080 --> 16:45.920
No more sliding at last. Much better.

16:52.360 --> 16:54.320
What are you looking at?
Guilty conscience?

16:56.600 --> 16:58.920
Sick of the slide?
Switched to the high bar now?

17:00.520 --> 17:04.440
Yes, I'm on the high bar!
I'll show you how it's done!

17:14.359 --> 17:16.079
- Are you mental?
- Are you a doctor?

17:16.160 --> 17:17.240
What's going on?

17:20.560 --> 17:22.200
Should we keep analyzing the movie?

17:22.280 --> 17:24.839
Or should the class watch
your awesome performance?

17:41.640 --> 17:42.600
You're back!

17:44.960 --> 17:46.640
What's wrong? Did you fall?

17:48.000 --> 17:51.480
- Weiwei, I need your comfort!
- What happened?

17:51.560 --> 17:54.400
I ran into that annoying guy, Cao Guang.

17:54.480 --> 17:55.720
He made me look like a fool,

17:55.800 --> 17:58.680
and I had to sit on the high bar
for an entire class.

17:58.880 --> 18:00.200
Walking back here,

18:00.280 --> 18:03.080
I got the most double-takes in my life.

18:03.720 --> 18:07.480
Then you didn't get hurt in vain.
You're a celebrity now.

18:08.200 --> 18:10.320
Well? Is it bad?
Do you need medical attention?

18:10.840 --> 18:14.920
No, I'll be fine.
Next time I see that jerk,

18:15.000 --> 18:16.600
he'll get it!

18:18.360 --> 18:20.560
You seem to be okay. Lay down for a bit.

18:20.840 --> 18:22.760
If you're still in pain, let me know.

18:38.000 --> 18:40.720
Zhenshui is afraid to reply to my message?

18:45.360 --> 18:47.040
What are you doing here, Luwei Weiwei?

18:47.120 --> 18:49.200
Isn't Yixiao Naihe in a face-off
with Zhenshui Wuxiang!

18:49.280 --> 18:50.120
Aren't you going?

18:53.360 --> 18:54.480
Face-off?

18:56.040 --> 18:58.680
You've heard, right?
Let's go. Come with me.

19:12.280 --> 19:15.040
How come it's just Yixiao Naihe?
Why isn't Zhenshui Wuxiang here?

19:15.120 --> 19:16.360
Has he chickened out?

19:17.000 --> 19:20.240
I don't think
Yixiao Naihe can win honorably today.

19:20.800 --> 19:22.640
They're all players.
Why would that matter?

19:23.240 --> 19:25.120
Zhenshui Wuxiang can only win by wealth.

19:25.400 --> 19:27.920
Anyway, Zhenshui Wuxiang had it coming,

19:28.000 --> 19:29.120
for making that video.

19:29.680 --> 19:32.800
I'm so excited
that I get to see Yixiao Naihe battle.

19:32.880 --> 19:34.560
I get to see master skills.

19:34.640 --> 19:36.360
I'm ready to record this.

19:36.440 --> 19:39.520
My hardware isn't up to par.
Send me the video later.

19:39.600 --> 19:40.720
Sure.

19:45.880 --> 19:47.280
Mrs. Nai, you're finally here!

19:48.080 --> 19:49.120
What's going on?

19:49.200 --> 19:51.440
Why is he suddenly battling
Zhenshui Wuxiang?

19:51.720 --> 19:53.520
You don't know about the video?

19:55.680 --> 19:57.520
Naihe is doing this because of the video?

19:58.240 --> 20:00.600
Of course! This is serious.

20:00.680 --> 20:03.520
If Naihe doesn't destroy Zhenshui Wuxiang,

20:03.600 --> 20:05.720
how will he hold up his head in the game?

20:05.800 --> 20:08.560
Yes! At least knock off
two grades of his cultivated status.

20:09.200 --> 20:12.320
Two grades?
Battling doesn't affect cultivated status.

20:13.000 --> 20:15.520
Battling doesn't, but face-off does.

20:15.600 --> 20:17.200
Didn't you see
Naihe's letter of challenge?

20:20.600 --> 20:21.960
I only just logged on.

20:23.000 --> 20:24.520
He sent the letter of challenge yesterday.

20:25.160 --> 20:27.600
The system reports on Zhenshui Wuxiang's
reaction every five minutes.

20:28.080 --> 20:30.760
Zhenshui Wuxiang is online,
but he's afraid to accept the challenge.

20:33.000 --> 20:35.040
Zhenshui Wuxiang
won't accept the challenge.

20:35.640 --> 20:38.240
He and Naihe may both have
the best equipment,

20:38.680 --> 20:40.400
but face-off is suicide for him.

20:40.640 --> 20:42.000
His status is so high.

20:42.080 --> 20:44.560
Dropping a grade will take him
forever to recover,

20:44.640 --> 20:45.480
not to mention two grades.

20:47.280 --> 20:48.840
He has no choice.

20:48.920 --> 20:51.200
Naihe is wagering two rounds.

20:51.680 --> 20:53.960
If Zhenshui Wuxiang wins one round,
and he wins the face-off.

20:54.560 --> 20:56.760
Naihe will never mention the video again.

20:56.840 --> 21:00.480
Plus, Naihe voluntarily gave up
two pieces of artifact equipment.

21:01.040 --> 21:03.800
If Zhenshui Wuxiang can't agree
to those terms,

21:03.880 --> 21:05.560
is he still a man?

21:05.800 --> 21:07.600
No-show is worse than losing.

21:07.680 --> 21:10.000
Insidious, indeed.

21:10.440 --> 21:12.400
Zhenshui Wuxiang
and the Xiaoyu clan are here.

21:12.480 --> 21:13.400
It's showtime!

21:13.840 --> 21:17.200
Here they are. The Xiaoyu clan is here.

21:19.800 --> 21:21.000
It hasn't been this bustling in forever.

21:21.080 --> 21:22.920
Yugong, want to place a bet?

21:23.000 --> 21:25.960
Why are we betting?
You think Naihe would lose?

21:26.520 --> 21:31.720
Shallow! I'm betting on how many minutes
it will take for Naihe to finish him off.

22:28.120 --> 22:29.440
Naihe has gone invisible.

22:31.040 --> 22:33.040
That's how the master rolls.

23:14.280 --> 23:17.640
Oh, no. He's been hit with
Naihe's Swing Rope. He's doomed!

23:18.880 --> 23:20.400
Why can't he get free?

23:24.600 --> 23:26.920
Wind-to-cloud, Naihe's group attack skill!

23:43.000 --> 23:44.320
It's over already? So fast!

23:44.800 --> 23:46.880
I didn't know Zhenshui was so mediocre.

23:47.440 --> 23:50.560
How tedious, unexciting,
and anti-climactic!

23:54.600 --> 23:56.840
- He's a bully!
- Zhenshui!

23:57.320 --> 23:59.440
Everyone knows Yixiao Naihe
can take on multiple players at once.

23:59.520 --> 24:02.680
Forcing Zhenshui into a face-off is like
ganging up on him, winning without honor!

24:02.760 --> 24:04.640
Seriously! It's so infuriating!

24:15.600 --> 24:18.200
Zhenshui, win or lose,

24:18.280 --> 24:19.800
you'll always be a hero to me.

24:20.960 --> 24:23.120
Don't worry about me, Yaoyao.

24:23.200 --> 24:24.240
Just stand by and watch.

24:28.000 --> 24:30.680
Yixiao Naihe,
Zhenshui is no match for you,

24:31.560 --> 24:32.960
but you went back on your word!

24:34.760 --> 24:35.640
What do you mean?

24:38.040 --> 24:40.720
- You said you'd give up two artifacts!
- Yaoyao!

24:44.440 --> 24:47.600
For the first round,
I didn't wear the ring.

24:51.400 --> 24:52.520
He didn't wear the ring!

24:52.600 --> 24:54.840
He still offed Zhenshui in no time.

24:56.080 --> 25:00.720
I truly pity Zhenshui Wuxiang.
How sad for him!

25:01.720 --> 25:04.440
It takes a month to regain
the loss of a grade in cultivated status?

25:05.000 --> 25:06.680
If he dropped two grades...

25:06.760 --> 25:08.960
My head hurts just thinking about it.

25:09.960 --> 25:12.840
So boring! It's a one-sided punishment.

25:13.280 --> 25:15.000
It pains me to watch it.

25:16.280 --> 25:19.720
For this round,
I'll fight you with one hand.

25:20.880 --> 25:23.360
That's not necessary.
I'll leave behind some equipment, too.

25:24.720 --> 25:25.600
Suit yourself.

25:56.000 --> 25:57.680
- Nice! Amazing!
- Sweet!

25:57.760 --> 25:59.960
- Incredible!
- Fantastic!

26:00.040 --> 26:02.760
- He's truly masterful! Incredible!
- Nice!

26:09.320 --> 26:11.120
What do you get out of this?

26:12.200 --> 26:15.160
If you have no self-respect,
how will others respect you?

26:15.760 --> 26:19.040
Fine. I've been shown my place.
I'll honor the bet.

26:19.520 --> 26:22.840
I will delete the video.
Yaoyao and I will make a new one.

26:23.320 --> 26:24.480
My cultivated status has already dropped.

26:24.960 --> 26:27.640
Let that be your compensation.
We don't owe each other anymore.

26:28.400 --> 26:30.640
It's fine. Just delete the video.

26:31.480 --> 26:32.320
Let's go.

26:37.920 --> 26:41.240
Naihe, Zhenshui Wuxiang
also left off some equipment.

26:41.320 --> 26:43.160
Did you expect he'd do that?

26:43.240 --> 26:44.640
Why should I bother?

26:45.440 --> 26:48.000
Naihe doesn't need to think
about him, okay?

26:48.560 --> 26:50.640
But you knocked two grades
off his cultivated status.

26:52.200 --> 26:54.280
I think he was prepared to die.

26:54.360 --> 26:56.080
It'll take him at least two months
to recover.

27:03.880 --> 27:05.320
You didn't think of a contingency plan?

27:05.400 --> 27:06.680
What if something went wrong,

27:06.760 --> 27:09.280
like the power went out,
and you couldn't get online?

27:09.360 --> 27:11.840
Would you let him get away with the video?

27:12.760 --> 27:17.960
If I lose, then I lose.
The missus is still around.

27:19.720 --> 27:20.680
What Naihe means,

27:20.760 --> 27:22.720
is if he loses,
he won't get involved anymore.

27:22.800 --> 27:24.280
But he didn't mention Mrs. Nai.

27:24.360 --> 27:26.160
Mrs. Nai is much stronger than Naihe.

27:26.800 --> 27:29.040
Whenever we fight a monster,
she's always the first to strike.

27:29.120 --> 27:30.920
Naihe is a deadbeat.

27:32.160 --> 27:33.840
- You're too kind.
- I took a look at the forum.

27:33.920 --> 27:36.400
He deleted the video.
That was pretty fast.

27:36.480 --> 27:40.320
Hey! He's really that compliant?

27:40.400 --> 27:42.120
Why do you sound disappointed?

27:43.000 --> 27:45.240
Of course, I am.

27:45.360 --> 27:48.080
If he doesn't delete it, we would...

27:49.520 --> 27:51.720
- Hack his computer.
- Delete his account.

27:51.800 --> 27:56.000
Then... I'll court Xiaoyu Yaoyao!

27:57.040 --> 27:59.200
You guys are awful!

27:59.560 --> 28:00.800
You're too kind.

28:00.880 --> 28:04.320
Compared to Naihe, we're like...
A drop in the ocean.

28:05.680 --> 28:08.840
"A drop in the ocean"?
Is that how you use that phrase?

28:11.080 --> 28:12.200
Don't mind the details.

28:13.040 --> 28:16.440
- Let's go, Weiwei.
- Where to?

28:17.800 --> 28:19.280
Somewhere without them.

28:23.160 --> 28:24.000
Hey...

28:28.680 --> 28:29.920
It's so pretty.

28:41.160 --> 28:42.960
You should've handled this yourself,

28:43.920 --> 28:46.080
but there are too many busybodies
in the public chat room.

28:46.880 --> 28:49.080
I thought it best to get it over with.

29:03.560 --> 29:06.560
Is Naihe trying to explain himself to me?

29:50.240 --> 29:51.680
Form an in-game marriage with me.

30:02.160 --> 30:03.640
You're all I need.

32:37.440 --> 32:39.760
Are you free today, Weiwei?

32:40.360 --> 32:42.320
You don't need to treat me to a meal.

32:42.520 --> 32:44.960
Well... Do you mind
if I walk with you for a bit?

33:00.040 --> 33:01.760
Hello? Who are you looking for?

33:02.440 --> 33:04.800
Weiwei? Who's this?

33:05.800 --> 33:09.960
- Cao Guang? Weiwei isn't here.
- Nice!

33:16.840 --> 33:18.480
Why are you so worked up?

33:21.760 --> 33:26.240
Is Cao Guang courting you, Weiwei?

33:27.160 --> 33:30.160
I think so. What should I do?

33:30.880 --> 33:33.040
What do you mean? Don't think about it.

33:33.120 --> 33:35.640
You cannot consider him, Weiwei.

33:35.720 --> 33:38.760
The photo incident proves
this guy has a flawed character.

33:38.840 --> 33:40.160
He only suspected the worst of you,

33:40.240 --> 33:42.760
because that's how he is. Right?

33:42.840 --> 33:45.680
Plus, he was so mean to me in class.

33:45.760 --> 33:48.120
He doesn't pass my standard, Weiwei.

33:48.200 --> 33:51.680
You cannot wager
your lifelong happiness on this guy.

33:52.040 --> 33:52.920
Wait.

33:53.280 --> 33:56.080
Why do I sense a lot of bad blood
between you and Cao Guang?

33:57.280 --> 33:59.080
I just don't like him.

33:59.840 --> 34:04.040
He may be the school's handsome genius,
second only to Xiao Nai,

34:04.440 --> 34:07.560
but if I don't think he's good enough,
I'm sure you don't think he's good enough.

34:08.199 --> 34:10.679
That's true.
I don't have feelings for him.

34:14.400 --> 34:16.199
On the other hand,

34:16.280 --> 34:20.679
if Cao Guang isn't good enough for you,
then you'll have to marry Xiao Nai!

34:21.560 --> 34:24.440
Erxi, will you be firm with your stance?

34:24.960 --> 34:27.719
Anyway, I think I've been clear with him.

34:28.000 --> 34:31.199
I don't like to be ambiguous
or waste his time.

34:32.679 --> 34:36.440
You're the best, Weiwei!
You hate my enemies, too!

34:37.239 --> 34:40.719
But what kind of guys are you into anyway?

34:41.480 --> 34:43.800
My head hurts.

34:45.239 --> 34:46.880
Don't you worry about me.

34:54.840 --> 34:57.040
Weiwei.

34:59.440 --> 35:02.800
- What is it?
- Come here, Weiwei! It's Xiao Nai!

35:02.880 --> 35:04.480
- Xiao Nai?
- Hurry.

35:04.560 --> 35:06.720
- Where?
- It's Xiao Nai!

35:07.440 --> 35:10.320
I heard he moved back on campus.
So, it's true!

35:12.200 --> 35:13.440
What does that girl want?

35:16.360 --> 35:18.040
Trying to defile Xiao Nai?

35:21.920 --> 35:23.160
Wow.

35:23.680 --> 35:26.280
I don't want anyone to defile
the god of our department,

35:27.120 --> 35:30.880
but he's just too aloof, too coldhearted.

35:31.600 --> 35:36.080
I can hear her heart shatter into pieces,
from this far away.

35:38.160 --> 35:41.360
Why are you spacing out, Weiwei?

35:42.680 --> 35:44.840
- I've got it!
- What?

35:45.800 --> 35:48.240
I know how to reject Cao Guang now.

35:49.000 --> 35:49.840
How?

35:51.520 --> 35:54.240
I'll use Xiao Nai as an excuse.

36:13.640 --> 36:14.840
There's no one sitting here?

36:16.480 --> 36:17.960
Um, no.

36:22.960 --> 36:25.480
Today's sweet-and-sour fish looks good.

36:38.800 --> 36:40.560
- Will you be free later?
- Yes.

36:41.200 --> 36:43.200
- I need to talk to you.
- Okay.

36:44.080 --> 36:44.920
You should eat.

36:59.360 --> 37:01.040
- I need to go.
- Okay.

37:07.720 --> 37:10.480
Cao Guang, I know your intentions,

37:11.200 --> 37:15.520
but I honestly don't think
we'd be compatible.

37:16.240 --> 37:17.320
I'm sorry.

37:17.400 --> 37:19.240
How would you know that, without trying?

37:20.760 --> 37:21.760
I don't want to waste your time.

37:22.920 --> 37:24.680
I don't think I'm wasting my time.

37:24.760 --> 37:26.880
No matter what,
I have the right to court you,

37:26.960 --> 37:28.480
until you change your mind.

37:30.040 --> 37:33.280
Sorry, Xiao Nai.
I have to use you as an excuse.

37:35.080 --> 37:37.640
My heart has already been given
to someone else.

37:38.920 --> 37:39.760
Who?

37:42.480 --> 37:46.800
Um... I've been wanting to date
a computer major,

37:48.160 --> 37:49.800
as we speak the same language.

37:50.400 --> 37:52.360
- So...
- Computer major?

37:53.600 --> 37:56.880
Yes, like Xiao Nai.

38:17.960 --> 38:20.080
What's going on?

38:20.160 --> 38:23.360
Genius Cao got rejected
by the computer department belle?

38:23.720 --> 38:24.880
What's it to you?

38:25.120 --> 38:27.080
As your fellow student journalist,
I must say,

38:27.160 --> 38:28.560
you have terrible taste!

38:28.760 --> 38:31.760
You fell for a department belle
with a taste for luxury cars?

38:31.840 --> 38:34.560
It's none of your business
that I got rejected.

38:34.640 --> 38:36.840
Also, the photo incident
was a misunderstanding.

38:36.920 --> 38:38.520
I already deleted it.

38:39.640 --> 38:41.520
You fell for her hard!

38:41.680 --> 38:42.800
She rejected you,

38:42.880 --> 38:46.200
- and you still defend her?
- I'm not defending her. It's the truth.

38:46.440 --> 38:50.360
I'm warning you. This is the end of it.

38:50.440 --> 38:51.920
Stop gossiping.

38:52.000 --> 38:53.920
Otherwise, you'll regret it.

38:57.240 --> 39:00.360
There's got to be dirt on Bei Weiwei.
I'll find it, if it kills me!

39:02.760 --> 39:05.120
Wait, no. I have to tell Yiran,

39:05.200 --> 39:06.800
Bei Weiwei likes Xiao Nai, too.

39:23.240 --> 39:24.120
Give it back!

39:24.520 --> 39:26.480
You didn't tell us, you got a girlfriend?

39:26.560 --> 39:28.440
Yeah. You should treat us to a meal!

39:28.520 --> 39:30.720
Nonsense! She's not my girlfriend.

39:30.800 --> 39:33.040
Not your girlfriend?
Why do you have her photo?

39:34.480 --> 39:36.960
Isn't this Bei Weiwei
from the computer department?

39:38.240 --> 39:39.960
That's your type?

39:40.040 --> 39:41.440
Enough! Stop messing around.

39:46.000 --> 39:49.360
She thinks you're not good enough?
Did she reject you?

39:49.720 --> 39:50.720
I just haven't won her over.

39:51.840 --> 39:54.920
Wow. Genius Cao has trouble
winning over a girl?

39:55.000 --> 39:56.000
That's unbelievable!

39:56.720 --> 39:58.880
You've had many girlfriends. Help him out!

39:59.600 --> 40:00.440
Okay.

40:00.760 --> 40:04.880
Cao Guang, play to a girl's interests,
if you want to win her over.

40:04.960 --> 40:06.880
Do whatever it is that she likes.

40:06.960 --> 40:09.080
Then, you'll have things to talk about.

40:09.160 --> 40:13.280
Once you have shared interests,
you should know how to do the rest.

40:18.000 --> 40:19.720
Gaming!

40:22.080 --> 40:23.440
That's so clever, bro!

40:23.520 --> 40:25.400
Dinner's on me! What shall we have?

40:25.480 --> 40:27.920
- Really? Hot pot, then!
- Let's go!

40:28.000 --> 40:29.080
- Go!
- Go!

40:42.680 --> 40:44.080
Yes, Class Leader Cao?

40:44.160 --> 40:47.160
You live in Number One Girls' Dormitory?
Can you do me a favor?

40:49.880 --> 40:52.400
Find out Bei Weiwei's avatar handle.

40:52.480 --> 40:54.520
I'll delete your truancy record
for this month.

40:56.440 --> 40:59.680
- Deal! I'll handle it.
- Thanks.

41:02.200 --> 41:03.160
Want to play ball, Cao Guang?

41:03.240 --> 41:05.000
- Sure. Be right there.
- Okay.

41:07.480 --> 41:10.960
Go.

41:11.560 --> 41:13.040
Nice shot!

41:14.800 --> 41:16.760
I'm done. This is pure torture.

41:16.840 --> 41:17.840
I want to team up with Nai!

41:17.920 --> 41:20.240
I've been patient with you.
How dare you despise me?

41:20.320 --> 41:22.240
What was that? Say it again!
I'll beat you silly!

41:22.320 --> 41:24.160
You and what army?

41:25.480 --> 41:27.080
- In-fighting.
- In-fighting!

41:27.160 --> 41:29.120
- Don't mind them. Let's play.
- Okay.

41:29.200 --> 41:30.360
- Guard him!
- Guard him!

41:30.920 --> 41:31.920
- Guard him!
- Guard him!

41:41.240 --> 41:42.720
Isn't that the computer major guy?

41:46.080 --> 41:46.960
Xiao Nai?

41:57.160 --> 41:58.000
You're Xiao Nai?

41:59.800 --> 42:00.760
That's me.

42:04.000 --> 42:05.080
Care to play?

42:06.480 --> 42:07.320
It'd be rude to decline.

44:38.480 --> 44:40.920
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
